  "system": {
    "description": "<p>This brass circlet focuses the powers of the Mark of Detection, granting the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>The wearer activates any Least Dragonmark power effects without expending Power Points.</p></li><li><p>If he has the Lesser Mark of Detection, he can reduce the Power Point cost to activate any Lesser Dragonmark powers by 2 (to a minimum of 1).</p></li><li><p>When using the <em>@UUID[Compendium.swade-fantasy-companion.swade-fc-powers.Item.sXrRk20IIFPhxkC0]{detect arcana}</em> power of the Mark of Detection to see through <em>conceal arcana</em>, he automatically reduces any penalties applied by the power or the Strong Modifier by 2.</p></li><li><p>He gains a +2 bonus Notice rolls.</p></li></ul><p>A character must attune the <em>diadem</em> by wearing it for 24 hours before its effects become active.</p>",
